  data:
    convoName: Seamstress - Max Trust
    lines:
    - character: Yume
      expression: 
      line: 'Orion, can I tell you something? '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: 'Sure. '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Yume
      expression: 
      line: "After I died, I just sat on that hill, watching the sunset, over and
        over again. I was mesmerized, but also so scared of change. My routine was
        the same all my life. To the point where l didn\u2019t know what to do after
        my end. "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: 'You were a hostage, indoctrinated into the culture of the Kanazawa Clan. '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Yume
      expression: 
      line: "That might be true, but it was my problem when I didn\u2019t want to
        look around town or see new places or talk or even move\u2026 It was you,
        Orion, who came along and pulled me out of that rut.  "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: 'At the time, I simply wanted your power, your skills that remain unmatched.  '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Yume
      expression: 
      line: "But that\u2019s no longer true, right? "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: "\u2026 "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: "I\u2019m not sure.  "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Yume
      expression: 
      line: "That\u2019s what you said to me when we first met. It was why I wanted
        to come with you in the first place. I was bent on changing your morals.
        Well\u2026 it was also because I wanted to get back at you for killing me.  "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: 'You would have been right to. '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Yume
      expression: 
      line: "That being said, you took me on a journey where I saw beautiful sights
        I didn\u2019t even know existed and met people with wild stories, people
        who shared their lives. Those moments made me realize how big the world is,
        and how much there is for me to explore! You\u2019re the connection that
        started it all.  "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: "\u2026 "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: 'I... have learned much from you, Yume. Your curiosity at the world...
        it was something that I never had, even at your age. I had always been simple-minded,
        always focused on the things I thought mattered most. But I see now that
        not everything is black and white. '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Yume
      expression: 
      line: "So, we both have something to learn! You\u2019ll keep bringing me along? "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: 'I suppose you are more than just your powers. '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
